{"id": "1414696396078186527", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "content": "thank you for the feedback though, that's quite helpful! I believe the standardized name now is \"Koum\", so all instances of that should be fully consistent in chapter 4 now (I have not had the chance to go back and revisit Ch3 to make sure there aren't any unusual bits there)\n\n\"guys\" is unfortunately something of a byproduct of English not having good plurality pronouns so using \"you guys\" tends to be a default in translation in lieu of more elegant options...I didn't specifically check for that as an issue, but if you could let me know any specific instances that you felt were jarring or characters who say it that seems out of character for them, I can revisit it for sure", "timestamp": "2025-09-08T19:38:24.613000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-08T19:52:22.344000+00:00"}
